				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>There has never been a vegan human society because it&#8217;s a pretty deadly diet. So no vegan organized religion. Veganism is a new religious behavior, associated with harm/care and also purity/pollution.</p>
<p id="comment-like-1780" data-liked=comment-not-liked class="comment-likes comment-not-liked"><a href="https://carcinisation.com/2014/11/22/why-cultural-evolution-is-real-and-what-it-is/?like_comment=1780&#038;_wpnonce=ca139e02ac" class="comment-like-link needs-login" rel="nofollow" data-blog="71183487"><span>Like</span></a><span id="comment-like-count-1780" class="comment-like-feedback">Like</span></p>
