				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Really? I don&#8217;t think so. I see it as expounding on what I wrote originally&#8230;</p>
<p id="comment-like-1784" data-liked=comment-not-liked class="comment-likes comment-not-liked"><a href="https://carcinisation.com/2014/11/22/why-cultural-evolution-is-real-and-what-it-is/?like_comment=1784&#038;_wpnonce=e913e28658" class="comment-like-link needs-login" rel="nofollow" data-blog="71183487"><span>Like</span></a><span id="comment-like-count-1784" class="comment-like-feedback">Like</span></p>
