				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/2014/11/22/why-cultural-evolution-is-real-and-what-it-is/?like_comment=1789&#038;_wpnonce=f53766cdbf&#038;replytocom=1784#respond' data-commentid="1784" data-postid="353" data-belowelement="div-comment-1784" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to JayMan'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
