		<li id="comment-1785" class="comment byuser comment-author-tgreernm even depth-6 parent highlander-comment">
			<article id="div-comment-1785" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cc7ab97617f4dc31189c5a938f8a2ad7?s=42&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-42' height='42' width='42' />						<b class="fn">T. Greer</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://carcinisation.com/2014/11/22/why-cultural-evolution-is-real-and-what-it-is/#comment-1785">
							<time datetime="2014-12-10T12:47:32-08:00">
								December 10, 2014 at 12:47 PM							</time>
